.-----------------------------------------------
. Supply & Inventory Period Control Routines
.-----------------------------------------------
. Read Control File Information
.-----------------------------------------------
RINPECON  READ      CONTROLF,TWENTY3;*129,SNCODFYR,SNCONOPR
          READ      CONTROLF,TWENTY4;HAPER1,HAPER2,HAPER3,HAPER4:
                    HAPER5,HAPER6,HAPER7,HAPER8:
                    HAPER9,HAPER10,HAPER11,HAPER12
          READ      CONTROLF,SIXTY3;*75,HAPER13
          MOVE      SNCODFYR,SIPECYR
          MOVE      SNCONOPR,SIPENUM
          RETURN
.------------------------------------------------------------
. Determine Period from Date
. Input   - SIPEDATE
. Output  - SIPEYEAR,SIPEPER,SIPELOC
.------------------------------------------------------------
RSIPE000  READ      CONTROLF,TWENTY3;*129,SNCODFYR,SNCONOPR
          MOVE      SNCONOPR,SIPENUM
          MOVE      SNCODFYR,SIPECYR
.
          UNPACK    SP70,SIPEYEAR,SIPEPER,SIPESDT,SIPEEDT
          MOVE      ZERO,SIPELOC
.
          PACK      KEY14,SIPEDATE,SP70
          CALL      RSSIPE2
          CALL      RKSIPE2
.
          MATCH     SIPESDT,SIPEDATE      * in date range ?
          IF        @LESS
            MOVE      ONE,OVRCD
          ENDIF
          RETURN
.
